column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release July 2018 Software v.3.9.5 2018-08-15
Nutrient data for: CADBURY DAIRY MILK CHOCOLATE TABLET HAZELNUT, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210373717
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: MILK**, sugar, cocoa butter, vegetable fats (palm, shea), cocoa mass, dried glucose syrup, bulking agents (glycerol (from sunflower), sorbitol), glucose-fructose syrup, fat-reduced cocoa, emulsifiers (E442, E476, SOYA lecithin, sunflower lecithin), roasted HAZELNUT paste, dried whole MILK, MILK fat, dried skimmed MILK, dried whey (from MILK), HAZELNUT oil, flavourings. **The equivalent of 426ml of fresh liquid milk in every 227g of milk chocolate. MILK CHOCOLATE: MILK SOLIDS 20% MINIMUM, ACTUAL 23%.CONTAINS VEGETABLE FATS IN ADDITION TO COCOA BUTTER..  MAY CONTAIN OTHER NUTS, WHEAT. Date available: 11/10/2017 Date last updated by company: 07/26/2016
